snippet.title: Snakes & Ladders - PlayStation 4 Gameplay
snippet.description:
This one is a simple game of snakes and ladders and it's actually pretty harmless. I did a review for the PS4 version on InfiniteBacklog, so feel free to take a look. It's one of the better Sabec Limited games, but not by much.

Review: https://infinitebacklog.net/users/aklim95/reviews/snakes-and-ladders--1

Developed and published by Sabec Limited
Also available on Nintendo Switch.
